Sonto turned around, to see Timothy's new form.  Cryrid followed, and with a glace of the glowing white body, was stunned with amazement.  Elil stood behind Timothy, still in shock of what happend.  Timothy raised his head, so his blue eyes glared at the two evil beast.<br>
&quot;Hello Boys.&quot; <p>

